=== Purchase Information === Product Title: Eyebrow Stamp, Eyebrow Stamp Shaping Kit, Eyebrow Stamp Stencils Kit, Waterproof,Long Lasting, Eyebrow Makeup Powder Kit, Eyebrow Definer for Women (Black) Review Date: 2022/05/11 Store: ALIVER Average Rating: 3.6 Product Details: {'Brand': 'ALIVER', 'Item Form': 'Powder', 'Finish Type': 'Natural', 'Material Feature': 'Natural', 'Package Information': 'Tube', 'Package Dimensions': '4 x 2.2 x 1 inches; 1.59 Ounces'} Review Text: I loved that there are so many brow shape stencils to choose from!
The powder had a very velvety feel! It stays put once applies and looks so great!
Love love love! Review Title: Love the many brow shape options and the powder stays put! Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: DmHirmg Ice Face Roller, Upgrated Ice Roller for Face and Eye, Facial Beauty Ice Roller Skin Care Tools, Food-Grade Leak-Proof Silicone Cube, Reusable Face Massage, Silicone Face Ice Mold for Face (Green) Review Date: 2022/05/20 Store: DmHirmg Average Rating: 4.1 Product Details: {'Item Form': 'Ice', 'Brand': 'DmHirmg', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Package Information': 'Roller', 'Package Dimensions': '6.22 x 5.16 x 1.46 inches; 2.4 Ounces', 'UPC': '734257211246', 'Manufacturer': 'DmHirmg', 'Country of Origin': 'China'} Review Text: I use it on my face opened up, and sometimes I use it as is closed if I don't want a huge mess!
I've used it as an ice pack for my kiddos boo-boos as well! Little and does the job! Review Title: Multiple uses for this cute little ice roller! Rating: 5.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Eyebrow Stamp Stencil Kit Brow Stencil Kit One Step Brow Stamp and Shaping Kit Kit Waterproof Eyebrow Stamp Shaping Kit, Natural Eyebrow(Blonde) Review Date: 2022/07/06 Store: Lizioo Average Rating: 3.4 Product Details: {'Brand': 'Lizioo', 'Item Form': 'Powder', 'Finish Type': 'Natural', 'Product Benefits': 'Waterproof, Sweat Proof', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Package Dimensions': '5.91 x 5.79 x 1.3 inches; 3.84 Ounces', 'UPC': '771077312517'} Review Text: I like the idea of stamping for people who have little to no eyebrows ie older generation.

I bought for my mom, she has grey hair and is still trying to use black eyeliner, it's a Mess she looks like she has caterpillars on her face.. so I jumped at the chance to get a stencil kit for her I thought blonde would be a good fit since there really isn't a grey color selection.

The kit itself has a great variety or stencils, and even better pens for contouring and eyebrow wax.
Unfortunately the blonde color isn't more like a brownish/blonde and not in a good way more dingy. The pen was on the drier side. The stamping ink was moist and stayed put - even after I tried several times to remove it from her brow. So it would be a good longer term solution if you got the right color match . Review Title: Colors seem to be a little off Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: YouClean 300 Antibacterial Travel Hand Soap Sheets - Pocket/Purse/Wallet/Backpack -Great for Outdoor Camping or Daily Use (Tea Party) (Tea Party) Review Date: 2022/07/10 Store: YouClean Product Description: ['Brand:', 'YouClean', 'Item Form:', 'Sheet', 'Formulation:', 'Concentrated plant-based soap', 'Scent:', 'Tea Party (Chamomile, Green Tea, Tea Tree)', 'Package Box Size:', '2 x 1 x 1.5 inch', 'www.shopyouclean.com', "We are changing our packaging. No more small plastic cases! Our new packaging is 100% biodegradable paper. All 300 sheets are tightly packed in 3 tiny paper boxes (100 sheets/box) which nicely fit in any purse/wallet, handbag, and kids' pack-backs. Check out our 9 scent collections: - Tea Party - Citrus Collection - Purple Heart - Pink Pamper - Red Passion - Blanca Elegance - Seaside Vacation - The Adventure - The Nonsense (unscented)"] Average Rating: 3.6 Product Details: {'Item Form': 'Sheet', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Brand': 'YouClean', 'Scent': 'Tea Party', 'Material Type Free': 'Plastic Free, Chemical Free (Not containing Sulfate, Phosphate, Paraffin, Phthalate, Gluten, Lead, Palm Oil and Mineral Oil)Plastic Free, Chemical Free (Not containing Sulfate, Phosphate, Paraffin, Phthalate, Gluten, Lead, Palm Oil and Mineral Oil) See more', 'Product Dimensions': '2 x 1 x 1.25 inches; 2.4 Ounces', 'UPC': '609670421100', 'Manufacturer': 'YouClean'} Review Text: I was happy these little squares pack such a good smell punch!
It suds enough I would say for a single small square of soap. But the residue defi sticks to your palms so you will need a good amount of water to rinse it off.

I took a star off because the listing says 400 sheets and I only for 200 - 4 packs of 50, so it differed from the listing information. Review Title: Perfect for travel or camping good scent and good suds Rating: 4.0 --------------------------------------------------

SUMMARY:  
This individual's purchase history indicates a preference for versatile, functional products that enhance beauty and convenience. Notably, they favor eyebrow makeup tools and skincare items, reflecting a keen interest in personal grooming. The positive ratings highlight enjoyment of multiple options (e.g., brow shapes) and the effectiveness of products (e.g., long-lasting formulations), while mixed ratings point to occasional dissatisfaction with color accuracy or product consistency.

Common themes include practicality, as seen in the multifunctional use of the ice roller (for both skincare and children's minor injuries) and the desire for products that cater to specific needs, such as age-related eyebrow solutions. 

In terms of quality, they appear to prioritize natural materials and effective results, showing sensitivity to packaging and product claims (i.e., misrepresentation of sheet count in soap). Price sensitivity is inferred from their engagement with varying price points without a clear preference for premium or budget options. 

Overall, core preferences center around innovative beauty and personal care solutions that offer convenience, effectiveness, and variety, alongside attentiveness to quality and product transparency.
